    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Driver-quality car in fair overall condition. It\u2019s presentable enough to use and enjoy, but it shows noticeable cosmetic wear, the interior has age and use throughout, and it should be expected to have the kinds of minor needs and upkeep common with an older used vehicle. Not a show car, but a workable example for someone looking for an affordable entry point and willing to live with imperfections.",
