      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for someone seeking dependable basic transportation without a major investment. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it still offers solid value as an inexpensive commuter, first car, or project opportunity. Priced to sell and ideal for buyers who want usable transportation at a budget-friendly price.",
