    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car looking for its next owner. It\u2019s not perfect, but it starts, moves, and offers a budget-friendly way into a set of wheels for someone handy or anyone after a simple project. Great as a runaround, learner car, or parts/project base. Priced fairly for what it is, with room for the right buyer to put their own touch on it. If you want something cheap and straightforward, come have a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or daily with good bones and plenty of usable life left. The engine pulls well, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels honest and composed for an older used car. Not cosmetically perfect, but that\u2019s reflected in the price\u2014this is a straightforward, affordable car that offers dependable transportation and a great platform for someone handy or looking for practical value. Well-suited for commuting, backup duty, or a light refresh.",
      "price": 5950.0,
