      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that feels like it still has stories left to tell. If you appreciate a vehicle with presence, personality, and real project potential, this one offers a chance to make it your own without stretching the budget. A great fit for a hands-on buyer, weekend tinkerer, or anyone looking for affordable transportation with a bit of soul.",
